### Flutterwave Withdrawal API Examples
### Use this file with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = your_api_key_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Get List of Banks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals/banks?country=NG
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Verify Bank Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals/verify-account
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "account_number": "1234567890",
  "account_bank": "044"
}

### Get Transfer Fee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals/fee?amount=1000&currency=NGN
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Initiate Withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "account_bank": "044",
  "account_number": "1234567890",
  "amount": 1000.00,
  "currency": "NGN",
  "narration": "Payment for services",
  "debit_currency": "NGN"
}

### Get Withdrawal Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals/status/WTH-1234567890-1234
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get All Withdrawals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals?page=1&per_page=20&status=SUCCESSFUL
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get All Withdrawals with Date Filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/withdrawals?date_from=2024-01-01&date_to=2024-01-31
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

